Council meetings and minutes

Join the conversation

Council meetings will be held in Council Chambers.

Council meetings will be livestreamed and a recording will be available to watch at a convenient time. Members of the public can address our Councillors by application.

Find out when the next Council meeting is scheduled and how to have your voice heard.

You can also have your say and share your thoughts on a range of initiatives, plans, policies and proposals on our over to you website.

About Council Meetings

Council meetings are open to the public and minutes are available to download.

Attending Council Meetings

All of the meetings of Council and its Committees are open to members of the public.

Livestreaming Council Meetings

All Council meetings are livestreamed via the Council website to enhance public access to the deliberations of Council.

Councillor Briefings

Councillor Briefings are livestreamed via the Council website to enhance public access to the deliberations of Council.
